          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Crumbling Foundations Small Business and Homeowners Assistance Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Emergency Management Agency to award grants&nbsp;for states to assist&nbsp;homeowners, small-business owners, and&nbsp;condominium associations in preventing, mitigating, and repairing structural damage to concrete foundations that contain pyrrhotite (an iron sulfide mineral linked to crumbling foundations).</p>]]></text>
